          </div>
        </div>

        <div className="text-xs text-teal-100 flex flex-col md:items-end leading-relaxed">
          <p><strong>A:</strong> Xuan Dinh, Bac Tu Liem, Hanoi | <strong>T:</strong> 0243 743 0666</p>
